comments.body:
@aditeyabaral Thanks for clarifying.
I got one more doubt here. Say a person didn't get any PPO, so he will be eligible for 2 offers right?

And, now (say) he gets an offer from Tier1 company. Will he be allowed to take the the offer? As far as I heard if he gets an offer from tier 1, he will be out of placement. And if he gets from Tier2 first then he is allowed for Tier1. So, is this two offers you are saying (Tier1 and Tier2), or the 2 offers can be from Tier1 ?
